# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment variables — apps/portfolio
#
# Convention (M0.0):
#   • Vite exposes ONLY variables prefixed with VITE_ to client code.
#   • This file documents every variable and is the only env file in git.
#   • Copy to `.env.local` for machine-specific values (git-ignored).
#   • The product is fully static (ADR-001) — expect very few variables.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Canonical site origin, used for absolute URLs in meta/OG tags (Phase 4).
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://example.com
